            <title>[LU-6572] simplify copytool kill and cleanup functions in sanity-hsm</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6572</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Trying to use search_and_kill_copytool() and search_copytools() functions to develop new sub-tests in sanity-hsm suite, found that copytool death delays were not handled and that this can be uniformized with what is done already in copytool_cleanup().&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;More sanity-hsm cleanup could also be to have both copytool_&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;setup,cleanup&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; use the same argument type, ie facetor host.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
